547
00:43:12,946 --> 00:43:18,418
[SPEAKER_02]: We have got to cut people's taxes and we have got to alleviate burdens on business.

548
00:43:18,979 --> 00:43:25,332
[SPEAKER_02]: Angela Rayner and the Labour Party, Keir Starmer confirmed this earlier this week, they are going to put up your taxes.

549
00:43:25,312 --> 00:43:25,773
[SPEAKER_02]: No it won't.

