553
00:43:31,082 --> 00:43:32,004
[SPEAKER_03]: That's a lie, Penny.

554
00:43:32,024 --> 00:43:35,970
[SPEAKER_03]: Your government have raised taxes to the record level in 70 years.

555
00:43:35,990 --> 00:43:36,631
