559
00:43:41,780 --> 00:43:43,924
[SPEAKER_02]: We will continue to cut taxes.

560
00:43:43,964 --> 00:43:45,847
[SPEAKER_02]: The country can afford it.

561
00:43:45,968 --> 00:43:48,552
[SPEAKER_02]: 2,000 pounds.

562
00:43:48,532 --> 00:43:54,640
