00:46:42,510 --> 00:46:44,112
[SPEAKER_08]: That links back to the previous question.

604
00:46:44,452 --> 00:46:49,578
[SPEAKER_08]: The population explosion has made housing, whether you buy them or rents, too expensive.

605
00:46:49,898 --> 00:46:52,581
