606
00:46:52,901 --> 00:46:56,745
[SPEAKER_08]: Getting rid of those subsidies on your energy bills would ease that.

607
00:46:57,025 --> 00:46:58,547
[SPEAKER_08]: But the big one's taxes.

608
00:46:58,527 --> 00:47:05,903
[SPEAKER_08]: Even during Tony Blair's time, the top rate of tax was 40p in this country, and it was paid by 1.5 million people.

609
00:47:06,545 --> 00:47:11,456
[SPEAKER_08]: By the end of 2027, 8 million people will be paying 40p tax.

610
00:47:12,077 --> 00:47:14,342
[SPEAKER_08]: So we're dragging more and more people

