00:48:10,051 --> 00:48:17,979
[SPEAKER_11]: Instead, they're having the worst of Westminster argument between them tonight, instead of being honest with you about the fiscal outlook going forward.

622
00:48:17,999 --> 00:48:20,661
[SPEAKER_11]: But there's also a conspiracy of silence on one other issue.

623
00:48:20,641 --> 00:48:22,425
[SPEAKER_11]: And that's Brexit.

624
00:48:22,445 --> 00:48:27,515
