633
00:49:24,556 --> 00:49:27,900
[SPEAKER_11]: Silence on £18 billion of cuts, silence on Brexit.

634
00:49:28,121 --> 00:49:30,844
[SPEAKER_11]: The public deserve better and the SNP will provide it.

635
00:49:30,824 --> 00:49:34,110
