[SPEAKER_02]: We have had to spend a lot of money on things like furlough.

672
00:52:29,260 --> 00:52:35,291
[SPEAKER_02]: That was the right thing to do, to keep jobs and livelihoods going, not just hand out welfare payments.

673
00:52:35,331 --> 00:52:39,960
[SPEAKER_02]: The pandemic has been expensive and we've also had terrible global shocks.

674
00:52:40,040 --> 00:52:42,745
