678
00:52:53,186 --> 00:52:59,420
[SPEAKER_02]: We have announced already we're making cuts on your taxes regarding your home, your pension, work.

679
00:52:59,761 --> 00:53:01,285
[SPEAKER_02]: We need to continue to do that.

680
00:53:01,365 --> 00:53:04,151
[SPEAKER_02]: If you get us, we will reduce your taxes.

681
