00:54:34,450 --> 00:54:38,234
[SPEAKER_08]: If we get a new kind of politics in Britain, we might just get some real change.

705
00:54:38,534 --> 00:54:45,662
[SPEAKER_08]: What we're being offered, frankly, are two parties promising the earth and nothing much will change, regardless of who gets in.

706
00:54:45,922 --> 00:54:46,423
[SPEAKER_08]: Although,

707
00:54:46,403 --> 00:54:52,791
